room_title: Escape room "The Apartment" by Escape the Room Indianapolis in Indianapolis
review: Did the Apartment with a group of six friends and my wife (along with two pick ups), escaped, and loved it. Isaac was a great host, we really needed his clues in the last 15 minutes.

room_title: Escape room "The Apartment" by Escape the Room Indianapolis in Indianapolis
review: So much fun! We absolutely loved it. We did the Apartment and it was so fun running around finding clues, even with the strangers we just met.

room_title: Escape room "The Apartment" by Escape the Room Indianapolis in Indianapolis
review: We did the Apartment and it was awesome! We have done a few others and this one was just as good! We plan to come back and try The Dig!! Highly recommend for a date night!
